election officials have certified 
the mayoral victory of hector luis acevedo whose 29vote triumph 
ends the prostatehood new progressive partys 20year lock on city 
hall 
the final figures announced wednesday gave 100525 votes to 
acevedo of the popular democratic party and 100496 for jose 
