report of it so i dont want to be too definitive about it but it 
seems that there were some further clarifications in it i welcome 
that but so far as its been reported to me they havent meet 
these conditions if they meet these conditions then were prepared 
for a substantive dialogue weve said that well continue to say 
that thats our position 
q mr secretary could you give us a bit more of an idea of what 
