mikhail s gorbachev urgently headed for home today to cope with 
the crisis of a devastating earthquake expressing confidence that 
superpower relations were on track after a summit with president 
reagan and presidentelect bush the american leaders expressed 
condolences and offered us assistance 
gorbachev standing on a windswept runway at john f kennedy 
