decide on a casebycase basis whether to seek the death penalty 
which congress approved in the recently enacted drug bill he added 
the district of columbia criminal code does not have a death 
penalty and all cases involving deaths and drugs would be 
prosecuted in federal court stephens office is responsible for 
prosecuting all serious criminal cases in this city of 625000 
