receiving 16000 from little and will remain in office snyder 
didnt attend the news conference 
all were going to say at this time is that he was offered a 
campaign contribution in that amount which he refused royals 
said adding that snyder never told mpampl officials they must settle 
the lawsuit or he wouldnt approve the rate hike 
littles wife helen little would only say he was out of town 
thursday and she didnt expect him to return before saturday wards 
secretary in dallas said he planned to issue a statement friday 
