major pending rate increase before the public service commission to 
pay for its share of the grand gulf nuclear power plant in port 
gibson 
the indictment notes that on sept 16 1985 the public service 
commission entered its order allowing a 147 percent projected rate 
increase over the first year or about 68 million 
