bought and he added that united gas has had several owners since 
the settlement was reached and could not comment on the indictments 
we had no knowledge of any illegal activity at the time the 
lawsuit was settled mpampl spokesman jim moore said he would not say 
whether any public service commissioner ever told the utility its 
rate increase wouldnt be approved unless it settled the lawsuit 
against united gas pipeline 
