lloyds the markets ruling body on wednesday after an internal 
disciplinary and appeals procedure 
all four were found guilty of discreditable conduct in 
siphoning off excessive slices of interest earned on premiums 
invested in certain insurance activities for themselves or their 
families lloyds said 
